org.hibernate.engine.spi

Interface SessionFactoryImplementor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, Closeable, EntityManagerFactory, HibernateEntityManagerFactory, Mapping, QueryParameterBindingTypeResolver, Referenceable, Serializable, SessionFactory
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SessionFactoryDelegatingImpl

    public interface SessionFactoryImplementor
extends Mapping, SessionFactory, QueryParameterBindingTypeResolver
    Defines the internal contract between the SessionFactory and other parts of Hibernate such as implementors of Type.
    See Also:
    SessionFactory, SessionFactoryImpl
